import React from 'react';
import {  View, Text, StyleSheet } from 'react-native';

const Layout = () => {
    return (
        <View style={style.container}>
            <View style={{
            height: 70,
            padding:10,
            width: '25%',
            shadowColor: '#000',
            shadowOpacity:0.2,
            shadowRadius:1,
            backgroundColor:'#f6d743',
            borderRadius:10
            }}>
            <Text style={{ textAlign: 'center', fontWeight: 'bold'}}>Positif</Text>
            </View>
            <View style={style.box2}>
            <Text style={{ textAlign: 'center', fontWeight: 'bold'}}>Sembuh</Text>
            </View>
            <View style={style.box3}>
            <Text style={{ textAlign: 'center', fontWeight: 'bold'}}>Meninggal</Text>
            </View>
        </View>
    )
}


const style = StyleSheet.create({
    container: {
        flex: 500 ,
        flexDirection: 'row',
        justifyContent: 'center',
        
    },
    box1: {

        height: 70,
        padding:10,
        width: '25%',
        shadowColor: '#000',
        shadowOpacity:0.2,
        shadowRadius:1,
        backgroundColor:'#f6d743',
        borderRadius:10
      
       

    },
    box2: {

        height: 70,
        padding:10,
        marginLeft: '5%',
        width: '25%',
        shadowColor: '#000',
        shadowOpacity:0.2,
        shadowRadius:1,
        backgroundColor:'#42e6a4',
        borderRadius:10
      
       

    },
    box3: {

        height: 70,
        padding:10,
        marginBottom:0,
        marginLeft: '5%',
        width: '25%',
        shadowColor: '#000',
        shadowOpacity:0.2,
        shadowRadius:1,
        backgroundColor:'#eb4559',
        borderRadius:10
       

    },
})

export default Layout;
